    <item>
      <title>杰夫·亚斯向雅培捐赠 400 万美元，创下德克萨斯州捐款纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/jeff-yass-gives-4-million-to-abbott-after-record-texas-donation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰夫·亚斯向格雷格·阿博特的竞选团队捐赠了 400 万美元，加上去年 12 月的一张 600 万美元支票，德克萨斯州州长办公室称这是该州历史上最大的单笔政治捐款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/jeff-yass-gives-4-million-to-abbott-after-record-texas-donation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 20:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯企业发现从中国获得付款越来越困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-sanctions-make-it-harder-for-russian-firms-to-get-paid-by-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯几家主要大宗商品出口商表示，自美国 6 月份扩大制裁标准后，以人民币进行的直接支付越来越多地被冻结或推迟，与中国的贸易已成为一场赌博。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/us-sanctions-make-it-harder-for-russian-firms-to-get-paid-by-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 20:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特别检察官正在对特朗普文件案件的驳回提出上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/special-counsel-is-appealing-dismissal-of-trump-documents-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国特别检察官杰克·史密斯向佛罗里达州联邦法院提交了上诉通知，质疑法官本周早些时候驳回对唐纳德·特朗普处理机密信息不当和妨碍司法公正的指控的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/special-counsel-is-appealing-dismissal-of-trump-documents-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯最高外交官赞扬特朗普和万斯在乌克兰问题上的立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russia-s-lavrov-praises-trump-vance-ticket-on-ukraine-war-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯最高外交官表示其倾向于共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普以及他的竞选搭档 JD 万斯，并称赞他们有意达成协议结束乌克兰战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/russia-s-lavrov-praises-trump-vance-ticket-on-ukraine-war-stance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前特朗普助手称中国威胁明显但台湾必须挺身而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-trump-aide-says-china-threat-is-clear-but-taiwan-must-step-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的前国家安全顾问无视对部分中国产品征收 100% 关税将加剧通胀的担忧，并呼吁与北京进行他所说的广泛“战略脱钩”，让人们初步了解了前总统重新执政后美国的经济和外交政策可能会是什么样子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-trump-aide-says-china-threat-is-clear-but-taiwan-must-step-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 19:21:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 向举报人颁发 3700 万美元奖励，以表彰其协助调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/sec-awards-whistleblower-37-million-for-aiding-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国证券交易委员会称，一位匿名举报人将因帮助金融监管机构调查不当行为而获得 3700 多万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/sec-awards-whistleblower-37-million-for-aiding-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:51:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登急于稳定陷入困境的竞选活动，却向左转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/biden-grasping-to-stabilize-beleagured-campaign-lurches-left</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登为稳定其连任竞选而采取的最新策略是向左转，希望通过提出雄心勃勃的新提案来消除医疗债务、限制租金上涨并对最高法院实施全面的新限制，从而获得进步派的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/biden-grasping-to-stabilize-beleagured-campaign-lurches-left</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:47:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>旧金山市长候选人希望通过减税刺激重返工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/san-francisco-mayor-hopeful-wants-tax-cut-to-spur-return-to-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山市长候选人马克·法雷尔制定了一项让员工重返市中心办公室的计划——但该计划不包括通勤福利或咖啡机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/san-francisco-mayor-hopeful-wants-tax-cut-to-spur-return-to-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国呼吁大学关闭，抗议政府职位导致六人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-17/urgent-government-urges-bangladesh-s-universities-to-close-after-6-die-in-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达卡，孟加拉国（美联社）——在校园暴力抗议活动造成至少 6 人死亡后，孟加拉国几所主要大学于周三同意关闭校园，抗议活动组织者宣布将关闭除基本服务以外的所有服务，示威者与警方之间的激烈冲突持续到深夜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-17/urgent-government-urges-bangladesh-s-universities-to-close-after-6-die-in-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 07:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
